  <brief_title>A Study To Investigate Markers Of Inflammation In Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Enabling Study to Investigate the Correlation of Biomarkers of the Activity of Inducible Nitric Oxide Synthase (iNOS) With Disease Activity and Treatment Response in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis(RA)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
